{"tid":657534,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"焦慮症share symptoms","createTime":"2018-05-08T07:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T08:53:57.000Z","uid":129825,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b9f25757aca02b69d113eeb89303fe7ad100a33f","tid":657534,"uid":129825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:49:16.000Z","msg":"我無睇過醫生，但我成日有以下特徵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<br />\n1. 去廁所明明鎖左門，去之前又會心慌慌起身check多次真係鎖左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. 成日覺得個髮紮唔實，會重覆周圍禁下睇下有無漏左未紮既頭髮，一個鐘check幾次<br />\n3. 同男友出街見到佢check手機突然微笑/甜笑就會心涼一涼，又突然覺得好嬲 會即刻check佢手機<br />\n5. 見到人whatsapp已讀不回會好驚佢嬲左<br />\n6. 成日覺得坐後面既同事會望到我扮工睇片，一有人經過就會即刻即刻alt+tab<br />\n7. 成日覺得自己突然老左好多，成日問朋友我有無老左<br />\n8. 成日覺得自己個degree好雞，唔想答人讀咩degree<br />\n9. 成日覺得上司黑面就係想炒我，果日會全日心慌慌<br />\n10. 有時會好開朗，有時又會覺得自己好無用<br />\n11. 成日擔心搵唔到下一份工<br />\n12. 養寵物見佢有一兩日成日洽眼訓就會驚佢病左<br />\n13. 成日覺得身邊既人唔鐘意我<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b946adff05b876d7b92e52d5a964aac983ac65","tid":657534,"uid":96535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"無左4."},{"pid":"feb4dc5b327dc81e87ae183381e738a5439b5695","tid":657534,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:55:38.000Z","msg":"睇下醫生好喎"},{"pid":"dea189dd924dceb29a117138bd0bb95239c2d545","tid":657534,"uid":129825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69b946adff05b876d7b92e52d5a964aac983ac65","tid":657534,"uid":96535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"無左4."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T07:57:46.000Z","msg":"4. 成日覺得自己有咩病咩病會成日google check symptoms against my body conditions"},{"pid":"e95e5f0c40a7b57608e33d06d23330be2402362e","tid":657534,"uid":129825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feb4dc5b327dc81e87ae183381e738a5439b5695","tid":657534,"uid":13802,"l